{"title":"我曾去过沙漠","date":"2018-04-14T10:19:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 14, 2018","L":"04/14/2018","MM-DD":"04-14"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/12/fcs3X8Dad7NjUEK.jpg","link":"2018/04/14/我曾去过沙漠","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.498Z","content":"<blockquote><p>先是缓缓下滑<br>\n然后快速坠落<br>\n埋入沙中</p>\n</blockquote>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>我曾去过沙漠<br>\n细沙在风中塑舞<br>\n连续的曲线<br>\n像是女人的胴体<br>\n光滑细索</p>\n<p>但我绝不敢停驻<br>\n——先是缓缓下滑<br>\n然后快速坠落<br>\n埋入沙中</p>\n<p>醒来的是绿洲初曦的露珠<br>\n还是随风而去的蜃楼<br>\n都只是黄粱一梦</p>\n","prev":{"title":"只为再见到你","link":"2018/04/16/只为再见到你"},"next":{"title":"我们都曾沉沦于孤独","link":"2018/01/27/我们都曾沉沦于孤独"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/14/我曾去过沙漠/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦 Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"},"reading_time":"95 words in 1 min"}